Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: P2PS HOLDS INITIAL EXCHANGE OFFERING.  The cyrptocurrency will host the official IEO on Lukki, VinDAX and other centralized exchange launchpads.  P2PS token, a cryptocurrency that assists users in their transactions on the decentralized, secure, and interference-free, peer-to-peer communication platform, this week excitedly announced they will be holding their Initial Exchange Offering (IEO) on Lukki and VinDAX. P2PS is approved for listing after IEO on other leading exchanges as well.  · Lukki — Round 1 started Sunday July 28, 2019, running until August 19, 2019, https://app.lukki.io/ieo-list/p2ps-round-1.  · VinDAX –               a. Round 1 on Tuesday August 06, 2019 for 24 hours https://vindax.com/project/5d3e5d19f4270806a1aa226f.html               b. Round 2 on Wednesday August 14, 2019 for 24 hours https://vindax.com/project/5d3e5f28f4270806a1aa602c.html  P2PS is a fully functional product that has no comparable substitutes, alternatives or parallels on a global level, acknowledged as “one of its kind in the world” (Sourceforge); and a much needed solution globally according to industry and ICObench experts. P2PS is the world’s first blockchain-powered, secure, pure peer to peer, interference-free, digital communications system platform designed for everyone with a need to securely store and exchange digital data such as private data, medical records, banking data and government classified data, among other sensitive digital exchanges. Such platforms today are simply nonexistent.  There are several proven use cases for P2PS. Some of the prominent client segments include Banking & Finance, Central Banks, Government & Defense, Digital Education & Delivery, Healthcare & Pharma, and other corporate sectors.  According to Jameel Shariff, the CEO and Council Member of P2PS, “banks alone spend over $500 Billion annually on digital data ‘security’. However, they are unable to protect the ‘privacy’ resulting in hacks and loss of data”. Jameel went on to state that “Project highlights include P2PS being a fully functional multipurpose system with several use cases, a captive market in over 200 countries, “one of its kind in the world” secure communication system that is intuitive to the end users’ habits and rewards based. A salient feature is that p2ps token replaces licenses within the system used by decentralized and centralized exchanges, banking & finance industry, the central banks, government & defense, digital education & delivery, healthcare & pharma, e-commerce transactions, token offerings, digital assets trading, etc.”.  Regulated by the P2P Solutions Foundation, an independent body authorized to create worldwide network of secure digital services and governed by the Foundation Council, the P2PS token will be used beyond the North American continent, into Europe, Australia, Asia, Middle East and the rest of the world eventually. The goal is to proliferate beyond the originally targeted 49 countries that provides a Serviceable Obtainable Market (SOM) of about 772 million users from the 1.5 billion potential users, which constitutes the Total Available Market (TAM) size.  For more information, please visit: https://www.p2psf.org/

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear dyrso,  Thank you for starting off your mischief with a baseless allegation.  1. Would you care to explain to us, and to the broader community, what is the definition of a word called scam so loosely used by you here on our thread? 2. Why would you want to try to defame our image and attempt to drag us down when all that our corporations have done since 2010, are currently doing, and will continue to do, is for the greater good of humanity? 3. Please let us know specifically if and when we had any business dealings with you of any kind. If yes, can you please provide evidence and post the proof for us and for everyone to see right here? 4. Are you one of those listing agents/scammers promoting fake volume exchanges charging hefty upfront fees that we have politely declined to deal with?  Please be aware that we, the admin team members of our project, take our business very seriously and will not succumb to ANY kind of blackmail attempts from ANYONE, no matter who in the world you are. The more you try to defame us, the more we shall emerge clean because we really have nothing to hide. The broader community here knows and understand the tough times we have gone through. What our team members are involved in is no small contribution to the global society and for the greater good of humanity at large, immaterial of race, color, religion, nationality, etc.  If you are one among those who desires to help the fake volume exchanges rip off various newly launched projects, you will realize very soon that we, the admin team members who have always helped many from other projects/startups fight scammers like you without expecting or asking for any compensation and even declining to receive rewards when offered, WILL FIGHT YOU AND ANYONE LIKE YOU tooth and nail, including in the courts of law if need be.  With that said, we suggest you either post some proof here or leave us alone and go your way in peace.  Best regards, Team P2PS, www.p2psf.org.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello again and greetings dear LuckyLuke79,  Thank you very much for your valuable opinion and support.  We like to take this opportunity to let you know that we are indeed grateful for your appreciation of our sincere efforts. We have been striving very hard to demonstrate, not just by words but by action, that we are, in your words, a "serious and professional team". We agree with you that "Even from small things we understand the big projects and the great people behind them".  FYI, and for that of our community, we like to bring to your notice that it has been very difficult for us to deal with the greedy scammers in the garb of listing agents representing or promoting fake volume exchanges. They voluntarily and without invitation approach us to use their services; and subsequently when their offers are turned down after our due diligence, resort to baseless allegations in possible attempts of blackmail.  Our endeavor, among other things, is to fight such greedy listing agents of fake volume exchanges. We have always taken, and will continue to take, prompt action against anyone perpetuating any kind of scam, as has already been demonstrated to our community of this great Bitcointalk forum.  Thank you again for your valuable support to our project dear LuckyLuke79.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project for the greater good of humanity. We look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS, www.p2psf.org.

Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: P2PS Contract Migration Completed Successfully.  Hello and greetings dear P2PS Community,  Thank you for your continued support.  P2PS initially targeted 49 high potential countries with the Total Available Market (TAM) of a little over 1.5 Billion end users, the Serviceable Available Market (SAM) of about 1.1 Billion and the Serviceable Obtainable Market (SOM) of about 772 Million users.  However, in the last year we have received some serious inquiries from several countries in other parts of the world. Based on global demand, the initially targeted market size of 49 countries has now expanded to over 200 countries.  Therefore, accordingly the total supply of tokens has increased from 100 Million to 10 Billion. Since the increase could not be reflected through modification of the previous P2PS Smart Contract we had to migrate to the new Smart Contract through an official process. The Etherscan team, after their due diligence, approved the migration.  Here are the details:  Old Smart Contract:️ https://etherscan.io/token/0x24c45187bf3c5338ab4c92858f7390800099d605    New Smart Contract:️ https://etherscan.io/token/0x4527a3b4a8a150403090a99b87effc96f2195047  Please visit www.p2psf.org to stay tuned for updates.   Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project for the greater good of humanity. Look forward to your support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS, www.p2psf.org.

Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Sharing here for your convenience, the entire message on Medium, as referenced in previous post above.   Update of P2PS Bounties on Bitcointalk.  P2P Solutions Foundation May 3  Hello and greetings dear P2PS Community,  Thank you for your continued support.  We would like to bring to your notice that ALL our bounties are either pre-paid and/or the P2PS tokens for bounty participants are held in escrow by a highly trusted and reputed Hero member of the Bitcointalk forum.  There have been incidents of one or two bounty participants claiming that they have not been paid for their efforts. We understand their concerns and would like to address them in a civilized manner.  On one hand we thank everyone of the bounty participants for their continued involvement and their patience in waiting for our ICO to reach hardcap. We are sure they understand the difficulties faced by not just our ICO but also several other ICOs during the extended bear phase now popularly known as the crypto-winter.  On the other hand we wish to assure everyone of the bounty participants on the Bitcointalk forum that at the end of ICO the tokens that they have earned, and as approved by their respective bounty managers, will reach their ERC20 wallets. We have absolutely no reason not to respect the decisions of the respective bounty managers. We do not stand to benefit in any way by cutting off the deserving participants of their earned tokens. On the contrary we believe in rewarding the honest and hardworking participants.  Here are a few screenshots of what we have claimed above.  1. Reward for honesty:    Source: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2386388.msg24545967#msg24545967  2. Message posted by a highly trusted and reputed Hero member of Bitcointalk forum confirming that 500000 P2PS are held in escrow.    Source: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2386388.msg26772690#msg26772690  TXID https://etherscan.io/token/0x24c45187bf3c5338ab4c92858f7390800099d605?a=0x659c5bf1dee7700ff9c2260c634503ef4c2c7972  Moreover, since the proof is in the pudding, all phase 1 qualified participants as approved by the bounty manager have received their respective tokens as earned. This can be confirmed from the following hash:  https://etherscan.io/address/0x659C5Bf1Dee7700Ff9c2260C634503Ef4C2c7972  We hope that these clarifications would rest our case and free us of any allegations hurdled towards us by one or two seemingly impatient members of this great Bitcointalk forum.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project for the greater good of humanity. Look forward to your support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Thanking you again, Best regards, Team P2PS, www.p2psf.org.   Source: https://medium.com/@p2ps/update-of-p2ps-bounties-on-bitcointalk-7ae03350877f

Body: Hello again and greetings dear bizdev,  Thank you for your query. Sorry for the delay in responding. We had to check with the relevant team members for clarification.  The major reason for abstaining from disclosing exchange names at this point in time is that we are still in ICO stage; and regulations restrict us from any such disclosure.  The logic behind this is two fold - one is that the regulatory authorities may construe such disclosure as P2PS trying to create FOMO and the other is that from the very beginning the team members, specially the top management, are against any strategy that may lead to FOMO resulting in speculators rather than HODLers jumping in.  Hope that answers your question. Please feel free to let us know if you have any other clarification or questions.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project for the greater good of humanity. We look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS, www.p2psf.org.

Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear Dime21  Thank you for your query, patience and support.  Anything that you exchange digitally with anyone, anywhere, is not private by any privacy standards; including information exchanged on your "private" intranet corporate networks. We are attempting to solve one of the biggest problems related to data security and privacy that has been identified as a global problem that is costing the world no less than about $500 Billion annually. Data security is extremely important to ALL banking institutions, government establishments, medical industry as well as corporate institutions. The biggest challenge encountered today is transferring sensitive digital information and assets from point A to point B without any other person having any kind of access to it. Body: Hello and greetings dear Adwarteq  Thank you for your query, patience and support.  The P2PS crypto-token is an ERC20 digital asset token on the secure Blockchain. It replaces the traditional license and transaction fees paid by both service providers as well as end users on various peer-to-peer networks e-commerce platforms. The P2PS crypto-token was developed by the P2P Solutions Foundation team.  The P2P Solutions Foundation is an independent body governed by the Foundation Council. The P2P Solutions Foundation has been authorized to create a worldwide network of digital services that encompasses an alternative working model to the traditional models of peer-to-peer networks. The alternative working models of peer-to-peer networks must be on Blockchain and compliant with Crypto technologies that are conclusively acknowledged as technologies of the future. Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear glasky,  Thank you for your observation and your queries.  We will attempt to answer your concerns briefly:  1. according to article 11.3 of our P2PS whitepaper, if the hardcap is not met, the ICO must continue till the hardcap is reached. 2. We did not have any softcap; only hardcap. However, it is some of the community members here who suggested that we have a softcap or we will look like a scam (although our project development started in 2010 and already much money has gone into coming to this stage). 3. We have already explained the reason for not having them; it creates FOMO and our team members do not want to entice anyone to purchase our tokens for speculation purpose. There was a time when such information was not available on public domain and websites needed to display that information. However, currently you just need to go to ethercan or ethplorer to get that information in a more detailed manner. If you desire to see how many tokens have been transferred etc. please check details on etherscan or ethplorer. 4. Every person is entitled to his/her opinion. No one has forced anyone and we will be the last project to entice anyone to participate through use of FOMO tactics. It seems to have become fashion to label any project a scam if one or the other component is not according to the persons desire, without due diligence or giving serious thought wholistically to the benefits the P2PS project brings to humanity which today is in the clutches of anti-social elements and hackers who are stealing your private information to make you lose your digital assets. Here is the global problem of a huge magnitude that P2PS are attempting to solve as per the FAQ section of the website www.p2psf.org:  Anything that you exchange digitally with anyone, anywhere, is not private by any privacy standards; including information exchanged on your "private" intranet corporate networks. We are attempting to solve one of the biggest problems related to data security and privacy that has been identified as a global problem that is costing the world no less than about $500 Billion annually. Data security is extremely important to both government establishments as well as corporate institutions. The biggest challenge encountered today is transferring sensitive digital information and assets from point A to point B without any other person having any kind of access to it.  Do you know of any other system that has addressed this issue? Every single system available today is vulnerable. Can you think of a system that you can confidently use to send private information such as your bank password to anyone else like your husband/wife/son/daughter etc? Please name it if you know one. If you cannot find one, kindly support our project to bring the P2PS system that has no comparable alternatives, substitutes or parallels to the 772 million serviceable obtainable market that has been identified in the whitepaper.  Please feel free to let us know if you have any other questions or clarifications.  Kindly spread the good word about our project for the greater good of humanity. We look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS, www.p2psf.org.

Author: yuvadeep
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: P2PS is a blockchain based platform where it supports all the network devices used for different transactions that can achieve on the secure and decentralized platform. Peer-to -peer communications are used in the government sector and defense, digital education, and distribution, medical and pharmacy, banking and finance. The P2P creates a platform where clients and end users come together. P2PS is a place where P2PS tokens are used to follow several payments methods that can be understand by the asset managers. To use this platform end users need to pay 2% as their entry payment, whenever they want to change then user receives a license in the platform. P2PS tokens are used to provide services, license fee payments etc on the other platform of P2PS. A P2PS token are extended afar like North America and provides Serviceable Obtainable Market (SOM).

Body: Absolutely dear bizdev.  Here it is.  Scientists have found a way to recognize fraudulent projects. The joint development of California, Michigan, and Stanford universities — ICORATING is designed to automate the process of analyzing and evaluating ICO projects, as well as to identify fraudsters and protect investors’ funds. Scientists have uploaded information about 2,251 ICOs that were conducted over the past two years. Further, they compared the duration of the existence of ICO projects and the changes in the rates of the digital currencies they issued, with information on the primary placements of the tokens (White Paper, information from social networks, information about the founders, etc.). Testing showed that the ICORating algorithm can detect ICO scammers with an accuracy of almost 83%.

Moreover, as explained earlier, our website recorded volumes which were genuine hits but very, very high compared to all days earlier. Therefore, the site was down for about 20 mins. Anyone could face this problem. We all learn from our shortfalls and our team members worked around it quickly.  The unprecedented traffic reflects on the effectiveness of our digital marketing efforts rather than on our core team and core platform that has nothing to do with an ICO landing page hosted on a third party web hosting service. Guess lots of our members are mixing the matters and misunderstanding what is being offered by the P2PS system. We urge you to kindly take a look at our one-pager and pitch deck if you are unable to find the time to review the details in our whitepaper.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about your project. We look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear tophe15,  Thank you for your queries.  We have already stated earlier and shall, for your convenience state again, that we planned to sell 50M tokens through a few phases of ICO, not just this one. However, in this phase itself we have achieved just over 25M which is 50% of target. There are participation from public as well as large institutions. Anyone who is able to understand and value their security is contributing. We do not want to create fear of missing out in anyone. This is not an "investment" you are making to speculate but participating or contributing for the greater good of humanity. We are not interested in just numbers, we need some level headed people who are willing to understand the system and buy the tokens for their utility.  Having said that, we never anticipated our site volumes to be this large. Over the last few days, our site has been receiving traffic from all over the world, at unprecedented levels. Therefore, our relevant team members are already in talks with the service provide to further upgrade the dedicated server bandwidth. Due to the weekend they are unable to do anything much. This should be resolved in the next day or two. Please accept our apologies for any inconvenience caused. The site is the same at https://www.p2psf.org Kindly continue to spread the good word about your project. We look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Global Problem: Anything that you exchange digitally with anyone, anywhere, is not private by any privacy standards; including information exchanged on your “private” intranet corporate networks.  P2PS Purpose: The purpose of our ICO is to bring you a secure system through which you can exchange confidential digital assets or files with absolutely no interference from any third party; not even a network or systems administrator.  What Can P2PS Do That Others Don’t? P2PS is a pure peer-to-peer platform which safeguards, for example, your medical records, banking information and other sensitive digital assets, during exchange between two parties. Such platforms today are simply nonexistent.  Usage of P2PS Token: The P2PS utility token is designed to be used by members within the P2PS platform. It primarily assists in transactions on the decentralized, secure and interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platforms used in Government & Defense, Digital Education & Delivery, Medical & Pharma, Banking & Finance, and other corporate sectors. Subsequently, P2PS tokens will replace traditional licenses on other systems such as Electronic Learning Inc.’s educational system, Pan Excels eLearning solutions, among others.  Why P2PS Token? When you purchase P2PS Tokens, you are contributing directly into the new economy that has been designed for your benefit. Please be advised that you are neither investing in a company nor in the creation of a company or corporation. We have crossed those stages and are offering P2PS utility token that you will eventually need if you prefer to use our secure, interference-free communications platform.  Procuring P2PS Tokens helps grow the economic ecosystem built around the secure, peer-to-peer, interference-free communications platform. You are helping build an extremely secure and strong network of interference-free communication systems with faster processing and a perpetual record of transactions. This process also streamlines financial actions into efficient and highly secure processes.   What Has Been Done So Far? The secure, interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platform’s venture started in 2010 and has been self-funded to completion. In November 2017, we launched P2PS token and released the token in pre-ICO that is now an ongoing ICO.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: P2PS — Economic Value Integrated into Secure Communication System.    P2PS is the world’s first Blockchain-powered, secure, pure peer-to-peer, interference-free digital communication platform designed for everyone with a need to securely store and exchange digital data such as private data, medical records, banking data and government classified data, among other sensitive digital exchanges. Such platforms today are simply nonexistent.   MISSION  P2P Solutions Foundation enjoys a shared mission with ELI and ISI of being committed to effectively and consistently deliver world class, high quality, outstanding products, applications and services to its client’s at the most cost effective and reasonable price. Together, we anticipate meeting customer expectations by understanding client requirements, keeping pace with latest innovations through research and by engaging in sustainable best practices.  VISION  P2PSF endeavors to attain the individual and collective goals by:  § Cultivating partnership relationships with all stakeholders and clients, instead of being mere supplier or service provider;  § Motivating team members through incentives and reward programs, in addition to treating them as partners thereby bringing out the best in them, resulting in maintaining service excellence;  § Advancement of goals to enrich community and preserve the client confidentiality ecosystem.  FUNDAMENTAL TECHNOLOGY  will focus on providing:  A) Transactions that facilitate centralized digital services utilizing P2PS at peer-to-peer platform level;  B) Decentralized service for P2PS users. A set of tools aimed at lowering the barriers to embracing and integrating with the P2PS system for all stakeholders;  C) Implementing an efficient P2PS Rewards System.   Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project. We look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great week ahead.  Thanking you for your time and efforts,  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear negancoin,  Thank you for your observation and for your query.  We need to clarify that ELI and P2PS are NOT one company and in the near future are NOT going to become one company. These are two distinct entities following different jurisdictions. ELI is a client of P2PS that will use P2PS platform and tokens. Mr. Jameel A. Shariff is the co-founder and current CEO of ELI.  On the one hand Mr. Jameel was selected to head P2PS because of his extraordinary abilities, qualifications, experience including but not limited to handling multinational & multicultural teams as well as exposure to global markets and to different cultures. It was necessary for P2PS to have someone who is an extraordinary visionary with exceptional leadership qualities, dedicated to the success of the project.  On the other hand, Mr. Jameel is a strict administrator and directs work with uncommon zeal and motivation levels. His determination to get the right things done from the start and in the right manner is commendable. We as a team enjoy working with him due to his flexibility and understanding. However, when he sets rules he ensures they are not broken; not even by himself.  Moreover, although the landing pages are similar, the main site of ELI is very different. On the landing page of ELI, please scroll all the way down to the red ribbon to visit the main site.  We hope that the above clarifies the points raised by you. Please feel free to let us know if you have any other questions or seek any clarifications.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project. Look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great week ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear contractus325,  Thank you for your sensible query.  You have asked a question that is not easy for us to explain in a few sentences. Therefore, for the first time on this forum, we are forced to direct you to our whitepaper that has all possible details that we could provide you on the workings of our unique system. Kindly visit www.p2psf.org for the documentation. We suggest you start with the one pager and move on to the pitch deck. Thereafter you may want to review the details in whitepaper.  However, for your convenience, we are pasting here the information contained in the one pager.    Global Problem:  Anything that you exchange digitally with anyone, anywhere, is not private by any privacy standards; including information exchanged on your “private” intranet corporate networks.  P2PS Purpose:  The purpose of our ICO is to bring you a secure system through which you can exchange confidential digital assets or files with absolutely no interference from any third party; not even a network or systems administrator.  What Can P2PS Do That Others Don’t?  P2PS is a pure peer-to-peer platform which safeguards, for example, your medical records, banking information and other sensitive digital assets, during exchange between two parties. Such platforms today are simply nonexistent.  Usage of P2PS Token:  The P2PS utility token is designed to be used by members within the P2PS platform. It primarily assists in transactions on the decentralized, secure and interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platforms used in Government & Defense, Digital Education & Delivery, Medical & Pharma, Banking & Finance, and other corporate sectors. Subsequently, P2PS tokens will replace traditional licenses on other systems such as Electronic Learning Inc.’s educational system, Pan Excels eLearning solutions, among others.  Why P2PS Token?  When you purchase P2PS Tokens, you are contributing directly into the new economy that has been designed for your benefit. Please be advised that you are neither investing in a company nor in the creation of a company or corporation. We have crossed those stages and are offering P2PS utility token that you will eventually need if you prefer to use our secure, interference-free communications platform.   Procuring P2PS Tokens helps grow the economic ecosystem built around the secure, peer-to-peer, interference-free communications platform. You are helping build an extremely secure and strong network of interference-free communication systems with faster processing and a perpetual record of transactions. This process also streamlines financial actions into efficient and highly secure processes.  What Has Been Done So Far?  The secure, interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platform’s venture started in 2010 and has been self-funded to completion. In November 2017, we launched P2PS token and released the token in pre-ICO that is now an ongoing ICO.     Please feel free to ask for further clarifications.   Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project. Look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great year ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear BRNSTYLE,  Thank you for your sensible question.  Heres a little insight in response to your query.   The National Security Agency, too, has sounded the alarm on the risks to cybersecurity in the quantum computing age.    “Quantum computing will definitely be applied anywhere where we’re using machine learning, cloud computing, data analysis. In security that [means] intrusion detection, looking for patterns in the data, and more sophisticated forms of parallel computing,” according to Kevin Curran, a cybersecurity researcher at Ulster University and IEEE senior member.  But the computing power that gives cyber-defenders super-tools to detect attacks can be misused, as well. Last year, scientists at MIT and the University of Innsbruck were able to build a quantum computer with just five qubits, conceptually demonstrating the ability of future quantum computers to break the RSA encryption scheme.  That ability to process the zeros and ones at the same time means that no formula based on a mathematical scheme is safe. The MIT/Innsbruck team is not the only one to have developed cybersecurity-breaking schemes, even on these early machines; the problem is significant enough that representatives of NIST, Toshiba, Amazon, Cisco, Microsoft, Intel and some of the top academics in the cybersecurity and mathematics worlds met in Toronto for the yearly Workshop on Quantum-Safe Cryptography last year.  Source: https://techcrunch.com/2018/01/05/the-quantum-computing-apocalypse-is-imminent/?ncid=rss&utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+Techcrunch+%28TechCrunch%29   Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project. Look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great weekend.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello dear Arvilaine,  Greetings,  Thank you for your observation and for your query.  Our team members prefer for participants and contributors to understand our system and its related offering. Once they have understood the project, then they could voluntarily contribute depending on their individual preferences. That way they take an informed decision. The other way of putting up a show with a jazzy website or live updates of tokens sold would probably act as "enticing" a participant who may follow the herd mentality rather than taking a knowledgeable, well informed decision. We have always preferred the former to the latter and would continue to seek well informed decision makers rather than contributors who are influenced by someone else participating. In short we do not believe in creating FOMO (fear of missing out) in you as a basis of your participation.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project. Look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great week ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello dear cammie16,  Greetings,  Thank you for your observation and for your query.  Our team members prefer for participants and contributors to understand our system and its related offering. Once they have understood the project, then they could voluntarily contribute depending on their individual preferences. That way they take an informed decision. The other way of putting up a show with a jazzy website or live updates of tokens sold would probably act as "enticing" a participant who may follow the herd mentality rather than taking a knowledgeable, well informed decision. We have always preferred the former to the latter and would continue to seek well informed decision makers rather than contributors who are influenced by someone else participating. In short we do not believe in FOMO (fear of missing out) as a basis of your participation.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project. Look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great week ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello dear liliiaolivia2017,  Greetings,  Thank you for your query.  Global Problem:  Anything that you exchange digitally with anyone, anywhere, is not private by any privacy standards; including information exchanged on your “private” intranet corporate networks.   P2PS Purpose:  The purpose of our ICO is to bring to you a secure system through which you can exchange confidential digital assets or files with absolutely no interference from any third party; not even a network or systems administrator.  What Can P2PS Do That Others Don’t?  P2PS is a pure peer-to-peer platform which safeguards, for example, your medical records, banking information and other sensitive digital assets, during exchange between two parties. Such platforms today are simply nonexistent.  Usage of P2PS Token:  The P2PS utility token is designed to be used by members within the P2PS platform. It primarily assists in transactions on the decentralized, secure and interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platforms used in Government & Defense, Digital Education & Delivery, Medical & Pharma, Banking & Finance, and other corporate sectors. Subsequently, P2PS tokens will replace traditional licenses on other systems such as Electronic Learning Inc.’s educational system, Pan Excels eLearning solutions, among others.  Why P2PS Token?  When you purchase P2PS Tokens, you are contributing directly into the new economy that has been designed for your benefit. Please be advised that you are neither investing in a company nor in the creation of a company or corporation. We have crossed those stages and are offering P2PS utility token that you will eventually need if you prefer to use our secure, interference-free communications platform.  Procuring P2PS Tokens helps grow the economic ecosystem built around the secure, peer-to-peer, interference-free communications platform. You are helping build an extremely secure and strong network of interference-free communication systems with faster processing and a perpetual record of transactions. This process also streamlines financial actions into efficient and highly secure processes.  What Has Been Done So Far?  The secure, interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platform’s venture started in 2010 and has been self-funded to completion. In November 2017, we launched P2PS token and released the token in pre-ICO that is now an ongoing ICO.   Please continue to spread the good word about our project. Look forward to your continued support and participation.  Please have a great week ahead.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: P2P in term of transaction refers to electronic money transfers made from one person to another person without intermediation by a third-party; as a result, such transactions are faster, and the fee is much lower. But When a third party is removed from the transaction, there is a greater risk that the provider of the service may fail to deliver and that's why the P2P Solutions Foundation team are trying to build a secure Communication System by make it run on blockchain which are technologies of the future.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear all,  Just thought we will bring this to your notice since we have questions about bounty campaigns etc. We are ever grateful to our colleagues and all collaborators who we treat as, and nothing short of, our extended family. If you want to participate in our bounty and signature campaigns, feel free to do so through our bounty campaign thread. As of today all bounty campaigns are compensated via, what we believe to be, our highly undervalued P2PS tokens.  Heres the brief information, that is contained in "one pager" on our website www.p2psf.org as well as in the "pitch deck" and "whitepaper", pasted here for your convenience. Please feel free to visit our website for updated information and our ANN thread too where there is some interesting stuff posted from time to time.  Global Problem:  Anything that you exchange digitally with anyone, anywhere, is not private by any privacy standards; including information exchanged on your “private” intranet corporate networks.  P2PS Purpose:  The purpose of our ICO is to bring to you a secure system through which you can exchange confidential digital assets or files with absolutely no interference from any third party; not even a network or systems administrator.  What Can P2PS Do That Others Don’t?  P2PS is a pure peer-to-peer platform which safeguards, for example, your medical records, banking information and other sensitive digital assets, during exchange between two parties. Such platforms today are simply nonexistent.  Usage of P2PS Token:  The P2PS utility token is designed to be used by members within the P2PS platform. It primarily assists in transactions on the decentralized, secure and interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platforms used in Government & Defense, Digital Education & Delivery, Medical & Pharma, Banking & Finance, and other corporate sectors. Subsequently, P2PS tokens will replace traditional licenses on other systems such as Electronic Learning Inc.’s educational system, Pan Excels eLearning solutions, among others.  Why P2PS Token?  When you purchase P2PS Tokens, you are contributing directly into the new economy that has been designed for your benefit. Please be advised that you are neither investing in a company nor in the creation of a company or corporation. We have crossed those stages and are offering P2PS utility token that you will eventually need if you prefer to use our secure, interference-free communications platform.  Procuring P2PS Tokens helps grow the economic ecosystem built around the secure, peer-to-peer, interference-free communications platform. You are helping build an extremely secure and strong network of interference-free communication systems with faster processing and a perpetual record of transactions. This process also streamlines financial actions into efficient and highly secure processes.  What Has Been Done So Far?  The secure, interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platform’s venture started in 2010 and has been self-funded to completion. In November 2017, we launched P2PS token and released the token in pre-ICO that is now an ongoing ICO.   Look forward to your continued and participation.  Thanking you again, Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear Jedie22,  Thank you for your observation and your best wishes for the projects success.  Please keep us in your prayers. We need them as we go through some unexpected and unanticipated challenges in the form of broken promises made to us by folks we thought were credible enough to be trusted to honor their words over a handshake.  This too shall pass and we will emerge victorious from this stage as well. If we have been around self-sustaining and self-funding this project for eight years to completion, then no disappointment or challenge is too big for us to face. Knowing that not just our idea but also our efforts are being well appreciated by industry leaders and community members alike, I dont think one or two people trying to pull us down, like frogs in a well, will really make a dent on our project. What do you think? Am I making sense here? Do we have your support? If yes, then nothing else matters.  We shall list on exchanges sooner than anticipated, and we shall God willing roll out our platform sooner than we desired. The credit goes to 4 people namely Mr. David Drake, Mr. Ken Tachibana, Mr. Sean Brizendine and Mr. Sean Kirtz; each one of them a specialist and leader in his own way. Thank you gentlemen for your support and participation.  Look forward to your continued support and participation gentle folks.  Please have a wonderful holiday season and stay safe.  Best regards, Team P2PS.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear negancoin,  Thank you for your observation and compliments.  We have come this far travelling a long road by interacting with, and getting feedback from, a cross section of the population. The sample population surveyed gave a strong indication that what we started off to build is what the world at large needs as we go into the digital era of e-everything including e-governance, e-banking, e-learning, e-medicine, etc. In order to succeed, not just in the ICO phase, but also as an organization it is very important to be proactive. At this stage we are only able to allocate certain amount of time to communicate with you but we are sure as we go along and iron out some of the challenges faced, we shall be able to reciprocate and communicate with you in a better manner. Everyone will have hurdles and we are no different. Therefore, you can expect from us a response in a fair amount of time. There may be many factors keeping us from communicating with you more frequently. For example the last couple of days when I logged in, the forum was offline because the servers were down. This happened a few times and I got engaged with other activities. Thats just one small example of the ground reality.  Please continue supporting our project and participate. Best regards.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear UpsilonTrooper,  Thank you for asking. I too reacted in a very similar way when I heard that.  Absolutely. There are many David Drakes. Heres the brief profile of our own Mr. David Drake.   David Drake’s FULL bio on LDJ Capital Website:  Source: ldjcapital.com/executive-team   David Drake and his family office LDJ Capital and its partners, has acted as GPs and investors in fund-of-funds, realty funds, venture capital funds, seed funds, debt funds and hedge funds.  Mr. Drake's investments and private equity advisory at LDJ Capital currently has 50+ global directors and family office partners maintaining relations with institutions and family offices with $1.5 trillion in assets.   Mr. Drake and his family office manages and co-invests alternative assets with the top 30 out of his investments in The Soho Loft Media Group that has a 5000 family office and institutional investor reach. These top 30 have aggregate asset under management of $1.5 trillion with 40% from Asia, 30% from Europe and 30% from the Middle East.     Mr. Drake’s access to 100,000 investors is maintained through his media holding investment The Soho Loft Media Group which has produced and sponsored over 1100+ global finance conferences since 2002, ie events by institutional media leader Thomson Reuters, with speakers from Nasdaq, NYSE, KKR and Carlyle Group. Global investor relations, capital allocation, syndication and buy side advisory are augmented at LDJ Capital advisory division via The Soho Loft Media Group.   LDJ Capital Special Situations partners have invested $100 Million in Alibaba and Palantir and continues with its NYC partner at McCarter English to place $500M in pre-IPO companies such as Lyft, N3N, Klarna, Dianrong, Truecaller, Crowdfunder, MagicLeap, DropBox.  LDJ Capital Real Estate’s multi-family strategy is to acquire series A core rental properties in global gateway cities at a 4+ cap rate and turn them into a 10 cap repositioning with a 15% IRR.  The realty hotel division works with top 10 hotel operators and asset managers globally including pursuing its own hotel acquisitions and hotel conversions in NYC.   LDJ Capital invests and handles buy side advisory for institutional fund placement, mutual fund seeding, fintech Investments, data and risk analysis investments, natural resources from gold to oil revenue generating properties to operating minority and controlling stakes in, but not limited to, broker dealers, wealth management, hedge funds, transportation, finmedia to insurance.   Mr. Drake has been involved in technology, media, telecoms, realty, hospitality, cleantech, energy and social impact investments for more than 25 years. He is an advocate of digital automation investing in private equity, compliance, capital formation policies and the US JOBS Act which he lobbied for in the US Congress and the EU Commission. Because of his leading work in this space, he represented the US Commerce Department at the EU Commission in Brussels and Rome in 2012 and was invited to the White House Champions of Change ceremony in Washington, D.C. and as a speaker at the UK Parliament in 2013.   Privately, Mr. Drake has hosted the Harvard Business Club of NY at his home, produced Carnegie Hall concerts and raised funds for the charities Trail Blazers and Best Buddies for many years. As he resettled in NYC from years of traveling, he was honored March 2015 to become a board director for the New York City Opera and years as a board advisor for The Washington Ballet which allows him to work and advise US Ambassadors from, but not limited to Sweden, Dominica, Ukraine, Marshall Islands, Australia and Luxembourg.  Born in Sweden and fluent in six languages, Mr. Drake has an MBA in Finance and an MA in International Law and Economics from George Washington University in DC where he was awarded the Wallenberg Scholarship for academic merit.    Look forward to your continued support and participation. Please have a wonderful weekend.  Best regards.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear quimbi777651,  Thank you for your asking. So what happens when a person goes to a doctor for an analysis of any condition is that there are various tests carried out and reports generated. In the US we have a short name for it called patient privacy where such patient records are not disclosed to anyone, not even family, unless expressed permission is granted by the patient. So how does the doctor send those records to the patient? Email? Almost all the time, such records are never private simply because there is no secure, interference-free network as of now anywhere in the world that can be used to send such highly sensitive and confidential information between the doctor and patient. As we all know, no email, sms, whatsapp messages, telephone calls or for that matter ANY communication as of today that is interference-free. Someone or the other has possibly viewed the info or heard of it before its in your inbox. Isnt it? Therefore, it is imperative that your sensitive and confidential information should be exchanged only on a secure channel of communication. Hope I am making sense to you. Please feel free to let us know if we can further clarify.  Kindly continue to spread the good word about our project and we look forward to your continued support and participation.  Best regards.

Body: Hello and greetings dear moonfrost21,  Thank you for your observation and for asking some good questions.  Other than the press releases posted, our PR team has also undertaken much more PR activity which we have refrained from posting here. What we posted was just a sample of a PR that went viral and was on so many different news channels and sites. We have reached out to over 30000 journalists worldwide in the last few days. Our website has been recording hits from all over the world. We had over 140000 headline impressions only from one PR release and over 1000 recorded hits just from one site. These are just to name a few.  Electronic Learning Inc. was first incorporated in 2004 when Jameel co-founded it along with another group. Jameel also participated in co-founding Innovative Solutions International in 2010, this time with a totally different group. Therefore, you will find Jameel as the common person in the two groups. He was also selected to head the corporations as its CEO, an executive function outside of his shareholding and equity participation. However, they are two separate and distinct entities as of now.  Please feel free to let us know if you have any other questions or clarifications and please spread the good word about our ICO. Look forward to your support and participation.  Best regards.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello and greetings dear Mister.Satan,  Thank you for your query. It is indeed a sensible questions that involves method of communication that our platform essentially is.  Net neutrality, as defined by Wikipedia, "is the principle that Internet service providers must treat all data on the Internet the same, and not discriminate or charge differently by user, content, website, platform, application, type of attached equipment, or method of communication".  Whereas, we are a secure communication platform (method of communication if you may) that transmits your digital assets securely and without anyone on the network as much as accessing it or even looking at it during its travel to its destination. Such type of an interference free platform does not exist anywhere today, not even on "private" corporate intranets.  Please feel free to let us know if you have any further questions or clarifications.  Look forward to your support and participation.  Best regards.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Hello again dear Bizdev,  Absolutely. At the very design stage itself we considered all these aspects. That was a time when the iPads had just launched and the Samsung tablets were beginning to see the light of day. If these new technologies were being introduced, there would obviously be lots of people buying into them; and they were built to last. Therefore, with lessons learnt earlier from Microsoft's and Intel's annually updated OS as well as hardware (processors mainly), we did not want to take chances. Hence, we designed our systems to be capable of working on older models of computers, generally speaking.  Hope that answers your question.  Look forward to your continued support and participation.  Thanking you again, Best regards.

The market sampled had to be indicative of the end users; a huge task by itself. Subsequently the product had to user friendly too.  So to cut a long eight year story short, we now are at a stage where we have serious interest demonstrated by large institutional participation. For example Mr. David Drake, the founder and chairman of LDJ Capital manages assets of 1.5 Trillion USD. How many people could  possibly boast of numbers as big as those? And then again, the team comprises of a blockchain specialist namely Mr. Sean Brizendine, having been involved in blockchain from its very early days. Mr. Sean alone is instrumental in selling upto $20Million EQUIVALENT of P2PS tokens.  As you can see, there are large institutions interested and we would very much want to see some of our tokens bought by the general public too. Again, it depends on many factors. Most of the people today are running behind coins that have already run up a lot and are ready to correct. But isnt that the way the herd mentality works?  Hope I have been able to address some of your concerns and could now say we look forward to your support and participation.  Thanking you again, Best regards.

Author: p2psf
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: Anything that you exchange digitally with anyone, anywhere, is not private by any privacy standards; including information exchanged on your so called “private” intranet corporate networks.  The purpose of our ICO is to bring to you a system through which you can exchange confidential digital assets or files with absolutely no interference from any third party, not even an administrator.  Therefore, it is a pure peer to peer platform which safeguards, for example, your medical records, banking information, among other sensitive digital exchanges that today are simply nonexistent.  The P2PS crypto-token is designed to be used by members within the P2PS platform. It primarily assists in transactions on the decentralized, secure and interference free, Peer-to-Peer Communication System platforms used in Government & Defense, Digital Education & Delivery, Medical & Pharma, Banking & Finance, and other corporate sectors.  Since P2PS token is an ERC20 crypto-token and smart contract system built on the Ethereum blockchain it is easily transferable between users and platforms using ERC20-compatible wallets and is smoothly integrated into exchanges.

Author: Fire Rabbit
Title: P2PS-WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATION SYSTEM
Body: P2PS - WORLDS FIRST & ONLY SECURE, INTERFERENCE-FREE COMMUNICATIONS SYSTEM   P2PS Phase 2 ICO is going to start on April 2.    Follow Us _______________________________________________________________________________ ______________  Website|Whitepaper| Facebook|Twitter|Instagram|Bounty|Telegram   _______________________________________________________________________________ ______________     Introducing P2PS Token    The P2PS crypto-token is an ERC20 digital asset token on the secure Blockchain. It replaces the traditional license and transaction fees paid by both service providers as well as end users on various peer-to-peer networks e-commerce platforms. The P2PS crypto-token was developed by the P2P Solutions Foundation team.   P2PS Token- Development, Acceptance and Proliferation of P2PS Token  The P2P Solutions Foundation is an independent body governed by the Foundation Council. The P2P Solutions Foundation has been authorized to create a worldwide network of digital services that encompasses an alternative working model to the traditional models of peer-to-peer networks. The alternative working models of peer-to-peer networks must be on Blockchain and compliant with Crypto technologies that are conclusively acknowledged as technologies of the future.   P2PS token will be used on secure platforms. One such platform that has committed to embrace the P2PS token is the secure, interference free, peer to peer, digital delivery system (Push System), promoted by Innovative Solutions International Inc. (ISI). The P2PS crypto-token is needed by anyone desiring to use the Push System. The Push System was developed in 2010 by ISI, a research and development corporation incorporated in USA, in response to the huge gap in the closed or locked down computer systems market segment. The Push System, in short, is a High Speed Large Digital Data Package Transfer System on the secure peer-to-peer proprietary networks. The P2PS token will assist you in all your transactions on the decentralized, secure and interference free Peer-to-Peer Digital Delivery System that is used in Government & Defense, Digital Education & Delivery, Medical & Pharma, Banking & Finance, and other corporate sectors.  Currently and in the immediate term, the usage for P2PS tokens would extend beyond the North American continent to the Middle East, providing a Serviceable Obtainable Market (SOM) of about 110 million users from the 220 million potential users which constitute the Total Available Market (TAM) size. The current clients of P2P Solutions Foundation, among others, are Electronic Leaning Inc. (ELI), a pioneer in eLearning solutions (www.eli.education) and the ISI group consortium (www.isigroup.org). Since both ELI and ISI Group caters to education, the Government & Defense, Banking & Finance market segments, the P2PS token has immediate acceptability with a ready client base in North America, Europe and Australia as well as the Middle Eastern countries. Moreover, both ELI and ISI group are headed for diversification into other global markets such as Europe, South America, China, etc. providing P2PS tokens a wider market penetration.   Guaranteed business From ELI and ISI group clients  P2PS tokens have a high potential growth trajectory through ELI and ISI group clients business alone. Both ELI and ISI Group commands a decent annual license fee per user for their respective digital platforms. Since the P2PS tokens will replace their licenses, there would be several advantages accruing to both the corporations through migration of their licensing models to the Blockchain technology. On one hand, the migration to Blockchain and Cryptographic technologies would enhance their security features. On the other hand, the positively disruptive move would provide more freedom from restrictions, and further democratize capital in a meaningful way along with providing peace of mind for all stakeholders. Copyright infringements that are quite common in the Middle Eastern countries would not only be reduced but also eventually be eliminated.   Where To Buy And Store P2P Tokens  Subsequent to the launch of the P2PS pre-sale and ICO, which shall take place on the Ethereum Network, anyone desiring to acquire the P2PS tokens can do so using the major cryptocurrencies they own via P2P Solutions Foundation website. The P2PS Tokens will thereafter list on Bittrex, Poloniex, Coinone, Yobit, Liqui, Waves DEX, EtherDelta and Cryptopia among other prominent global crypto-exchanges. After acquiring the P2PS tokens, you can deposit them into an ERC20 standard token wallet such as MyEtherWallet, Meta Mask, Mist, Parity, Imtoken, etc. One of the many reasons you may want to acquire and hold the P2PS tokens is for use on the various secure peer-to-peer proprietary network platforms other than to trade on crypto-exchanges. Please feel free to let us know if you have any questions or clarifications and you will find us always at your service.  The reason you find only one product available currently in the shop section is so that we do not confuse some who may be only looking to contribute. Also, we are not a retail product company. Therefore, we have kept it as simple as possible, in line with our mission, for you and everyone to deal with us and contribute through our website.  Please feel free to let us know if we can answer any of your questions that are not already answered either on our website or whitepaper.  Thank you again and look forward to your participation in our project.
